# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Title & Description
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
title: "TopoSAM-Flow"
subtitle: "Weakly-Supervised Industrial Image Segmentation via Differentiable Variational Flow and Topological Priors"
abstract: |
  TopoSAM-Flow is a deep learning framework for weakly-supervised industrial 
  image segmentation. It combines the Segment Anything Model (SAM) for 
  pseudo-mask generation, differentiable variational regularization inspired 
  by active contour models, and topological constraints via persistent homology. 
  The method achieves high segmentation accuracy with only bounding-box 
  annotations, reducing annotation costs by 91% compared to pixel-level supervision.

